{"lastModified":1765464461474,"uri":"c::7819217464::vessel::d5cc24b5-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Gulet","Sailing"],"description":"Operating Area: Turkey\n\nWith her modern exterior lines tastefully governing the classical interior touches Tango Charlie is a very unique charter vessel for the East Med and great value for money. She offers excellent sailing performance for those interested in hopping from one location to another even in light winds instead of having to cruise under engine power. There is a very spacious aft master cabin which can be accessed from a staircase leading down from the starboard corner of the salon. In the forward section is a VIP cabin and two other double cabins, giving this vessel a total guest capacity of eight. Her design allows full view panoramic views no matter which section of the deck you may be standing on. On board you may find all the modern amenities including wifi, cable TV, entertainment system, games and plenty of water sports which are supported by a powerful tender. With a very experience captain and crew on board including an excellent chef able to offer delicious world cuisine, you are guaranteed to return for a second trip on board Tango Charlie.","blueprint":{"name":"TANGO CHARLIE","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc24b5-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::82bf8d40-a378-11f0-8237-07e9117c6be0/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc24b5-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::82c29a80-a378-11f0-a115-a98937e0d318/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc24b5-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::82afd5d0-a378-11f0-a114-a98937e0d318/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc24b5-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::82c18910-a378-11f0-bd54-896dee0f7558/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc24b5-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::82af1280-a378-11f0-a115-a98937e0d318/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc24b5-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb72